name: FloatingWindowPosition

properties.name: UPPER_LEFT
properties.description: Positions the window in the upper left corner of the screen.

properties.name: UPPER_MIDDLE
properties.description: Positions the window at the top of the screen midway between the left and right edges.

properties.name: UPPER_RIGHT
properties.description: Positions the window in the upper right corner of the screen.

properties.name: CENTER_LEFT
properties.description: Positions the window on the left side of the screen midway between the top and bottom.

properties.name: CENTER
properties.description: Positions the window in the center of the screen.

properties.name: CENTER_RIGHT
properties.description: Positions the window on the right side of the screen midway between the top and bottom.

properties.name: LOWER_LEFT
properties.description: Positions the window in the lower left corner of the screen.

properties.name: LOWER_MIDDLE
properties.description: Positions the window at the bottom of the screen midway between the left and right edges.

properties.name: LOWER_RIGHT
properties.description: Positions the window in the lower right corner of the screen.

description: Options for specifying the position of a movie's display window.
